title: Kaminey
overview: In the web series, Kaminey, three friends buy a rented house with the aim of selling all the items in it for a quick profit. However, in this web series, the owner finds out and kicks them out of the house. The three friends end up on the road with no place to stay. That's when they meet Sweety, a kind-hearted young woman who takes them in at an organization that helps homeless people. As they spend more time with Sweety, the three friends begin to develop feelings for her and each of them tries to win her affection.
